34:25.231 --> 34:27.360
He died a few years ago.

34:30.987 --> 34:34.277
I heard you were married once?

34:35.324 --> 34:37.284
But she died too?

34:37.284 --> 34:37.745
Yeah.

34:45.208 --> 34:45.659
I'm sorry.

34:59.849 --> 35:01.725
She's not good.

35:01.726 --> 35:03.016
But, you know, it's hard to know

35:03.019 --> 35:06.729
'cause she's such
a hypochondriac.

35:07.148 --> 35:08.058
Oh, my God.

35:08.065 --> 35:09.321
I'm fine, Mom, don't worry.

35:09.322 --> 35:11.735
Don't worry, you look terrible.

35:11.736 --> 35:12.566
What happened to you?

35:12.570 --> 35:13.320
Got in a fight.

35:13.321 --> 35:14.651
A fight?

35:14.655 --> 35:15.913
- So what's this?
- Have you seen a doctor?

35:15.914 --> 35:16.866
Jesus Christ, are you alright?

35:16.866 --> 35:17.866
Yeah Mom, that's where
I got the stitches.

35:17.867 --> 35:19.075
This is you working hard?

35:19.076 --> 35:20.285
I was working
hard, I had a gig...

35:20.286 --> 35:21.576
Partying all hours of the night,

35:21.579 --> 35:22.287
and then a fight?
Would you stop it!

35:22.288 --> 35:22.908
- Dad!
- What?

35:22.913 --> 35:23.753
What is this?

35:23.754 --> 35:24.828
What's what?

35:24.832 --> 35:25.872
It's a collection notice.

35:25.875 --> 35:26.833
It's not my fault if
you're out there buying...

35:26.834 --> 35:27.334
For you.

35:30.671 --> 35:32.589
What was I supposed to do?

35:32.590 --> 35:33.880
Close up for six months while

35:33.883 --> 35:35.342
I wait for the insurance money?

35:35.343 --> 35:36.553
We would have been finished.

35:36.554 --> 35:38.222
The insurance
came after a month.

35:40.598 --> 35:41.308
It came after six.

35:43.768 --> 35:46.518
After the recession hit
we started losing money.

35:46.520 --> 35:50.270
I thought things would turn
around in a year or so, but

35:50.274 --> 35:50.734
they didn't.

35:54.070 --> 35:57.110
And then that damn storm hit.

35:57.114 --> 35:59.074
I had to take out a loan.

35:59.075 --> 36:01.034
Put the business
up for collateral.

36:01.035 --> 36:02.795
I knew you wouldn't let me,

36:02.796 --> 36:07.037
so I told you the money came
from the insurance company.

36:07.041 --> 36:09.081
When the insurance check came,

36:09.085 --> 36:11.635
it covered only half the cost.

36:15.007 --> 36:18.257
I didn't want either of
you to know how bad it was.

36:23.891 --> 36:25.058
It's gonna be okay.

36:25.059 --> 36:27.099
You're gonna have to lay
off some of the part-timers,

36:27.103 --> 36:30.605
the rest get a 10% cut,
and no more overtime.

36:30.606 --> 36:32.726
10%?

36:32.733 --> 36:36.319
If we can re-finance,
make some sacrifices,

36:36.320 --> 36:37.450
we can get through this.

36:51.001 --> 36:52.001
I'm sorry, but the request

36:52.002 --> 36:53.752
for a loan modification
has been denied.

36:53.754 --> 36:55.588
What?

36:55.589 --> 36:56.758
We can make the payments.

36:56.759 --> 36:58.837
The loan is more
than 90 days past due.

36:58.843 --> 37:00.681
We have the right to
collect immediately.

37:00.682 --> 37:03.298
What does that mean,
"collect immediately"?

37:03.305 --> 37:06.516
The business was
put up as collateral,

37:06.517 --> 37:09.807
so we will assume
ownership and liquidate it.

37:09.812 --> 37:10.979
That's outrageous.

37:10.980 --> 37:12.020
It was in the
contract you signed.

37:12.022 --> 37:13.522
You will make less money than

37:13.524 --> 37:14.484
if you just let us
make the payments!

37:14.485 --> 37:17.026
I'm sorry, that is
the bank's decision.

37:17.027 --> 37:18.277
Well then I want
to talk to a manager.

37:18.279 --> 37:21.529
He'll tell you the same
thing, the decision is final.

37:25.786 --> 37:28.156
You better believe the
Better Business Bureau

37:28.164 --> 37:30.424
is gonna hear about this,
and our congressman.

37:30.425 --> 37:32.826
This is unheard of behavior.

37:32.835 --> 37:35.170
And you should be
ashamed of yourself.

37:35.171 --> 37:36.461
It's no wonder the
small businesses

37:36.464 --> 37:39.299
in this town are
packing up and leaving.

37:39.300 --> 37:42.510
I have shown you the numbers,
we are a viable business!

37:42.511 --> 37:46.511
This is the kind of place
this community needs.

38:02.031 --> 38:02.741
Dad said he'd
mortgage the house,

38:02.742 --> 38:04.570
Roger doesn't want the money.

38:04.575 --> 38:08.286
I mean this is gonna kill
my dad, maybe literally.

38:08.287 --> 38:11.077
We tried to get into Roger's
office, he wouldn't talk to us.

38:11.081 --> 38:12.749
Will you talk to him?

38:12.750 --> 38:14.330
And say what exactly?

38:14.335 --> 38:15.635
I don't know, but
he'll take your call,

38:15.636 --> 38:17.208
'cause he does
business with you.

38:17.213 --> 38:21.223
Sam, I want to help, but I
don't know what I could say.

38:22.426 --> 38:25.296
Maybe if you told him that
unless he modifies our loan,

38:25.304 --> 38:27.430
you won't go through
with the deal.

38:27.431 --> 38:28.141
Sam.

38:28.142 --> 38:30.350
We signed a contract.

38:30.351 --> 38:33.101
To be honest this hasn't
been a very good year,

38:33.103 --> 38:34.773
I kind of need to
make this deal.

38:34.774 --> 38:36.940
What happens if you don't do it?

38:36.941 --> 38:38.441
You lose business,
you lose your house?

38:38.442 --> 38:41.652
You said you, you
rebuilt after the storm,

38:41.654 --> 38:44.072
and you, you wrote a check.

38:44.073 --> 38:45.623
My family lost
everything we had.

38:45.624 --> 38:47.236
Yeah, I wrote a check.

38:47.243 --> 38:49.702
And you know how
I could afford to?

38:49.703 --> 38:50.953
By not writing the wrong ones.

38:50.955 --> 38:53.293
I'm not running a charity,
and I got a lot of money tied

38:53.294 --> 38:56.629
up in this deal, and you're
asking me to dump it for what?

38:56.630 --> 38:58.917
To help a restaurant
that's already gone under?

38:58.921 --> 39:00.801
To help a guy who
took a catering job,

39:00.802 --> 39:04.128
and wound up in a
fist-fight with his client?

39:04.134 --> 39:06.344
Look, I'm sorry if
this sounds harsh,

39:06.345 --> 39:07.685
but I'm a business man
and this is business.

39:07.686 --> 39:12.730
I know, I'm asking a lot,
and I'm sorry, but I have to.

39:14.103 --> 39:16.943
'Cause this is
everything for my family.

39:18.607 --> 39:19.057
Please.

39:26.574 --> 39:27.744
I'm sorry, son.

39:28.909 --> 39:32.039
You're asking for
something I can't do.

39:36.792 --> 39:37.672
Okay.

40:12.286 --> 40:13.156
Here.

40:22.212 --> 40:23.842
This what you
were saving it for?

40:23.843 --> 40:28.089
I was saving it for my
retirement, so maybe.

40:31.639 --> 40:35.058
I haven't lived a
day without that

40:35.059 --> 40:36.559
building being in our family.

40:40.731 --> 40:42.611
When I was growing up
your granddad fixed

40:42.612 --> 40:48.237
it my head that this was
the land of opportunity.

40:48.238 --> 40:49.568
This city is full of
people who think they're

40:49.573 --> 40:53.453
gonna hit it big one
day, how many of them do?

40:54.495 --> 40:57.295
Those things get
bigger and bigger.

40:58.415 --> 40:59.625
The rest of us?

41:07.675 --> 41:09.385
Here's to the house!

41:18.352 --> 41:19.232
Hello?

41:21.981 --> 41:22.731
How could you do that?

41:22.732 --> 41:24.771
It was a business decision.

41:24.775 --> 41:27.281
That was not a business
decision, and you know it.

41:27.282 --> 41:30.196
You're ruining these
people's lives over a look.

41:30.197 --> 41:32.367
You haven't looked at me
like that in such a long time.

41:32.368 --> 41:34.276
Roger, nothing happened.

41:34.284 --> 41:35.622
I didn't do anything.

41:35.623 --> 41:36.788
I don't want to hurt you.

41:36.789 --> 41:38.246
I'm sorry, I'm confused.

41:38.247 --> 41:39.457
You didn't do anything
'cause you don't want to,

41:39.458 --> 41:42.206
or you didn't do anything
'cause you're not allowed to?

41:42.209 --> 41:42.959
Which is it, Sarah?

41:42.960 --> 41:45.128
Roger.

41:45.129 --> 41:46.749
Come on you wanted
it to, just admit it.

41:46.755 --> 41:48.798
Roger, I want us!

41:48.799 --> 41:51.089
I want us to feel right.

41:51.093 --> 41:52.303
But we don't.

41:55.055 --> 41:57.640
Are you happy,
with me, right now?

41:57.641 --> 41:59.225
Yeah, yeah, of course I am.

41:59.226 --> 41:59.726
Truly?

42:02.187 --> 42:03.057
Yeah.

42:04.064 --> 42:05.694
Huh.

42:10.029 --> 42:12.155
Because I'm not.

42:12.156 --> 42:13.486
I'm not happy.

42:14.658 --> 42:16.698
And I don't think that
you are either, because

42:16.702 --> 42:19.542
you couldn't be, and do
what you did to that family.

42:19.543 --> 42:22.998
I made my own decision,
I don't regret it.

42:23.000 --> 42:24.250
And if you can't do that, then

42:24.251 --> 42:26.881
you need to figure
your shit out.

42:28.797 --> 42:32.507
I think we need to
spend some time apart.

42:34.511 --> 42:35.341
Sarah?

42:36.096 --> 42:38.176
I think we should separate.

42:38.182 --> 42:39.892
Officially.

42:41.351 --> 42:42.351
Just sit.

42:42.352 --> 42:44.270
Hold on, hang on, you
don't want to do this.

42:44.271 --> 42:45.151
I do.

42:46.273 --> 42:47.653
I'm sorry but I really do.

43:03.123 --> 43:04.373
What are you doing here?

43:04.374 --> 43:06.714
Tom told me what happened.

43:09.880 --> 43:10.800
I'm so sorry.

43:13.050 --> 43:16.220
That is not your fault at all.

43:20.057 --> 43:21.017
Want a drink?

43:21.517 --> 43:23.387
Understatement.

43:43.288 --> 43:44.788
I always had a plan.

43:44.790 --> 43:49.040
Everyday I woke thinking
of my restaurant.

43:49.044 --> 43:52.344
Thinking of the next
step to get there.

43:53.715 --> 43:54.595
And now,

43:57.678 --> 43:58.548
nothin'.

44:03.600 --> 44:05.730
I saw that in my dad, too.

44:07.437 --> 44:11.017
Everyday of his life
he had that restaurant.

44:12.609 --> 44:15.739
And today, part of
him was just gone.

44:21.326 --> 44:23.406
And I used to think
more than anything

44:23.412 --> 44:24.952
that I was different than him.

44:27.499 --> 44:27.959
We're the same.

44:31.295 --> 44:31.925
Exactly the same.

45:01.408 --> 45:02.448
Shit, what'd I miss?

45:02.451 --> 45:04.410
I was thinking,

45:04.411 --> 45:06.871
about you, your dad.

45:09.583 --> 45:12.418
Maybe your old place is gone,

45:12.419 --> 45:15.379
but what if you
opened up a new one?

45:15.881 --> 45:18.257
It takes a lot.

45:18.258 --> 45:18.708
It takes...

45:18.715 --> 45:20.301
Money?

45:20.302 --> 45:21.886
Yeah.

45:21.887 --> 45:24.217
Can this get you started?

45:29.811 --> 45:30.311
I can't take that.

45:30.312 --> 45:31.942
You can.

45:33.315 --> 45:35.735
You can use it to start over.

45:39.446 --> 45:44.026
Sarah, that's really
generous, but I can't take it.

45:44.034 --> 45:48.412
You had more than that
taken away from you.

45:48.413 --> 45:48.833
Please take it.

45:51.375 --> 45:53.459
I kind of need you to take it.

45:53.460 --> 45:55.710
What about Roger?

45:55.712 --> 45:57.002
It's my money.

45:59.716 --> 46:02.546
But it's from our joint account,

46:02.552 --> 46:05.302
so you might want
to cash it soon.

46:05.722 --> 46:07.142
Like, today.

46:11.144 --> 46:15.064
I feel like a teenager, sneaking
out of your parents' house.

46:15.065 --> 46:15.565
Sorry.

46:16.692 --> 46:20.402
Don't be, it's kind of awesome.

46:27.577 --> 46:29.497
- Hey.
- Hmm?

46:32.916 --> 46:33.366
Thank you.

46:50.600 --> 46:52.310
Ah!

46:52.311 --> 46:53.436
Who was that?

46:53.437 --> 46:54.597
Why is there
always someone there?

46:54.604 --> 46:56.605
You brought a girl here.

46:56.606 --> 46:58.266
No, it's not like that.

46:58.275 --> 47:00.568
Oh, you're lucky your
mom's not here to see that.

47:00.569 --> 47:01.777
Where'd she go so early?

47:01.778 --> 47:02.398
Work.

47:02.404 --> 47:04.280
What?

47:04.281 --> 47:05.321
She took a job as a bookkeeper.

47:05.324 --> 47:06.824
That was fast.

47:06.825 --> 47:10.375
Came as a surprise, but
she has friends there.

47:12.456 --> 47:13.326
So,

47:15.625 --> 47:18.215
what's it like with this girl?

47:21.548 --> 47:24.508
I want to talk
to you about that.

47:28.472 --> 47:29.310
Thanks.

47:29.311 --> 47:30.636
Take all the time you need.

47:30.640 --> 47:33.809
It's not by the water.

47:33.810 --> 47:36.270
No, no it's not by the water.

47:36.271 --> 47:38.811
Which means less storm damage.

47:39.691 --> 47:41.361
It's also the reason
Josh is willing

47:41.362 --> 47:42.900
to rent it to us for so little.

47:42.903 --> 47:44.653
If he couldn't make it here,
what makes you think you can?

47:44.654 --> 47:46.280
I think he was
going for Asian Fusion

47:46.281 --> 47:47.871
in a neighborhood that's
about seafood, comfort food.

47:47.872 --> 47:50.866
They gave it a year,
it didn't work out.

47:50.869 --> 47:52.999
Happens to the best of us.

47:57.501 --> 48:00.336
I like the bar.

48:00.337 --> 48:01.497
Would this be your
place or mine?

48:01.505 --> 48:03.965
It could be ours.

48:06.510 --> 48:08.219
Yeah, hotel's good?

48:08.220 --> 48:09.510
It's alright.

48:09.513 --> 48:11.183
I set up a few things.

48:12.432 --> 48:13.972
It's weird not
having you in the house.

48:13.975 --> 48:15.022
I know, I'm sorry,

48:15.023 --> 48:17.808
but this is what we
need to do right now.

48:17.813 --> 48:18.979
How long?

48:18.980 --> 48:20.689
I don't know, maybe for a while.

48:20.690 --> 48:21.980
We're not working, Roger.

48:21.983 --> 48:24.985
How do you know,
you're not even here.

48:24.986 --> 48:27.696
Listen, please, I just
need some time and space.

48:27.697 --> 48:29.115
Okay, for now, we're separated.

48:29.116 --> 48:30.116
Yeah, but Sarah, if we just talk

48:30.117 --> 48:31.617
about it it's gonna be fine.

48:31.618 --> 48:33.868
So I need you to stop this
stupid shit, just come back.

48:33.870 --> 48:37.080
I don't know if I want to.

48:40.961 --> 48:44.211
Look, I know you're scared,
but this place is smaller.

48:44.214 --> 48:46.924
Business is picking
back up all over town.

48:46.925 --> 48:48.975
Everything is being
repaired from the storm.

48:48.976 --> 48:51.719
And what about the next storm?

48:51.721 --> 48:54.557
We don't have enough to retire.

48:54.558 --> 48:56.518
Not with what we've lost.

48:58.437 --> 49:00.597
What if we lose this house?

49:02.774 --> 49:06.944
If you would take a regular
job, just for a few years,

49:06.945 --> 49:11.073
we could save money, we
could plan our retirement.

49:11.074 --> 49:12.784
Why risk everything?

49:14.661 --> 49:18.330
Because running a
restaurant is what I do.

49:18.331 --> 49:21.041
It's what I've always done.

49:21.042 --> 49:22.172
Without that, what am I?

49:24.671 --> 49:27.131
You're my husband.

49:29.676 --> 49:33.926
You had that restaurant 30
years, and it was beautiful.

49:37.726 --> 49:39.806
But it's over.

50:40.497 --> 50:43.957
Not many people call me
before eight A. M. And live.

50:43.959 --> 50:45.539
Everything you needed.

50:45.544 --> 50:46.504
Can I get in today?

50:46.505 --> 50:49.003
You're an eager motherfucker.

50:51.341 --> 50:51.791
Hey.

50:53.426 --> 50:54.586
You need a job?

50:57.514 --> 50:58.354
Yes.

51:14.739 --> 51:17.029
Yes!

51:17.033 --> 51:21.078
♪ I was born in the middle

51:21.079 --> 51:23.869
♪ Maybe too late

51:24.958 --> 51:28.208
♪ Everything good had been made

51:33.049 --> 51:36.839
♪ So I'd just get loaded

51:36.845 --> 51:41.015
♪ And never leave my house

51:41.016 --> 51:44.226
♪ Just takin' way too
long to figure this out

51:48.064 --> 51:52.114
♪ Know my name, know I mean it

51:52.902 --> 51:55.237
♪ It's not as bad as it seems

51:55.238 --> 51:59.368
♪ And we try in our
own way to get better

52:04.205 --> 52:07.295
♪ Even if we're alone

52:21.056 --> 52:25.016
♪ I hate talking about money

52:25.018 --> 52:29.146
♪ I don't want to
talk about love

52:29.147 --> 52:32.357
♪ I hate thinking I'm
not the same as I was

52:35.987 --> 52:39.987
♪ I lose my faith in people

52:39.991 --> 52:45.161
♪ Why even take the time

52:45.163 --> 52:46.793
♪ You've got your
problems, I've got mine

52:46.794 --> 52:48.790
Thank you.

52:48.792 --> 52:50.501
Come on in.

52:50.502 --> 52:51.382
Wow.

52:51.383 --> 52:53.918
We're pretty much there.

52:53.922 --> 52:55.589
Sam, it's amazing.

52:55.590 --> 52:56.715
Thank you.

52:56.716 --> 52:57.166
Have you ever met Josh?

52:57.175 --> 52:58.467
No.

52:58.468 --> 52:59.428
He's my best friend.

52:59.429 --> 53:01.507
Hi, how are you, Sarah.

53:01.513 --> 53:05.723
♪ Just try in our
own way to get better

53:07.018 --> 53:10.648
♪ Even if we're alone, hey

53:28.164 --> 53:30.044
I got it, I got it.

53:38.842 --> 53:41.552
Again, for the record
that was amazing.

53:41.553 --> 53:42.433
I had a great time.

53:44.556 --> 53:45.426
Maybe you should come up?

53:45.432 --> 53:47.732
I can show you the
clothing designs.

53:47.733 --> 53:48.926
Yeah, sure.

53:53.565 --> 53:55.023
Oh, you have,

53:55.024 --> 53:57.324
I think you have got some
spinach stuck in your teeth.

53:57.325 --> 53:58.358
Oh, my gosh.

54:00.905 --> 54:01.823
I get it?
No.

54:01.824 --> 54:02.703
No?

54:04.492 --> 54:04.950
Now?

54:04.951 --> 54:05.871
Not at all.

54:05.872 --> 54:07.745
Oh, my god.

54:07.746 --> 54:09.866
Here.

54:09.873 --> 54:10.831
Whoa, what, what are you doing?

54:10.832 --> 54:11.542
It's okay, I'm a professional.

54:11.543 --> 54:14.541
I've dealt with this before.

54:14.544 --> 54:15.794
Let me just show
you where it is.

54:15.795 --> 54:16.255
Oh, god.

54:16.256 --> 54:18.088
Right there.

54:18.089 --> 54:18.839
Here?

54:18.840 --> 54:19.670
To the right.

54:19.674 --> 54:21.175
One more.

54:21.176 --> 54:22.466
Did I get it?

54:25.054 --> 54:26.722
Good to go.

54:26.723 --> 54:29.099
Great.

54:29.100 --> 54:31.190
So, should I come up?

54:31.978 --> 54:34.728
I don't know.

54:34.731 --> 54:36.231
Why not?

54:36.232 --> 54:39.692
Because if you come
up, I might kiss you.

54:41.404 --> 54:43.363
Well, maybe you should
just kiss me here.

54:43.364 --> 54:45.784
Then you don't have to worry.

54:46.910 --> 54:48.740
You want to kiss me?

54:48.745 --> 54:49.745
After all that?

54:49.746 --> 54:51.366
Really?

54:57.086 --> 55:01.086
Look I know you got a lot
goin' on in your life right now,

55:01.090 --> 55:03.630
so I understand you need to...

55:26.449 --> 55:29.868
Okay, now I really
want you to come up.

55:29.869 --> 55:31.539
I'd love to come up.

55:33.248 --> 55:36.667
Ugh.

55:36.668 --> 55:37.538
Ah.

55:39.212 --> 55:41.632
See how you feel next time.

56:47.030 --> 56:48.030
So now you call me back.

56:48.031 --> 56:50.369
I just bounced a check,
a very important one.

56:50.370 --> 56:51.825
Well money can go very quickly.

